      <JapaneseText>ボーナス宝箱出現！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>To Do</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>先へ進め！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>To Do</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>６０秒以内に３０Ｋ．Ｏ．を決めて★に辿り着け！\n門番を倒すと失敗になるぞ！　注意せよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
